Title: Excelsis Dei
Plot: Mulder and Scully uncover strange occurrences in an elderly care home when one of the nurses is attacked by an unseen force she claims to be one of the 90 year old residents.
GuestStars: Frances Bay, Teryl Rothery, Eric Christmas, David Fresco, Sab Shimono, Tasha Simms, Sheila Moore, Jerry Wasserman, Jon Cuthbert, Paul Jarrett, Ernie Prentice
